### Sign In
# @name signin
POST {{apiUrl}}/auth/signin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "ibqn@gmail.com",
  "password": "rootme99"
}

### Get User
GET {{apiUrl}}/auth/user
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Sign Out
POST {{apiUrl}}/auth/signout
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Upload File (with inline content)
POST {{apiUrl}}/upload/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

Hello, this is test file content!
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### Upload File (from filesystem)
POST {{apiUrl}}/upload/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="daniel-roe-lpjb_UMOyx8-unsplash.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./daniel-roe-lpjb_UMOyx8-unsplash.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

