### List Uploads
GET {{apiUrl}}/upload/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get Upload
GET {{apiUrl}}/upload/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Delete Upload
DELETE {{apiUrl}}/upload/3
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get Image (Original)
GET {{imageUrl}}/{{imageId}}

### Get Image (WebP Optimized)
GET {{imageUrl}}/{{imageId}}?format=webp&q=30&w=200

### Get Image (JPEG Quality)
GET {{imageUrl}}/{{imageId}}?q=70

### Get Image (Resize Only)
GET {{imageUrl}}/{{imageId}}?w=400

### Get Image (PNG Format)
GET {{imageUrl}}/{{imageId}}?format=png&q=90&w=300
